		<part id="scaling">
			<title>Scaling API Initiatives</title>
			<slide id="scaling-is-hard">
				<title>Getting started is hard, scaling up is even harder</title>
				<img href="https://www.mckinsey.com/business-functions/mckinsey-digital/our-insights/how-to-restart-your-stalled-digital-transformation" title='"How to restart your stalled digital transformation", McKinsey Digital, March 2020' src="stalled-digital-transformation.png" class="fullsize"/>
			</slide>
			<slide id="programs-products-platforms">
				<title>API Programs connect Products and Platforms</title>
				<ul>
					<li><em>API products</em> are products with APIs built by individual teams</li>
					<li><em>API platforms</em> are tooling and infrastructure for API products</li>
					<li><em>API programs</em> optimize API production by managing the API platform</li>
				</ul>
			</slide>
			<slide id="program-areas">
				<title>API Program Areas</title>
				<ul>
					<li>API programs are essential for scaling API initiatives</li>
					<li>API programs have to cover various areas</li>
					<ul>
						<li><em>Strategic Alignment</em> for aligning with other initiatives and activities</li>
						<li><em>Organization &amp; Culture</em> so that teams can work effectively</li>
						<li><em>Awareness &amp; Adoption</em> so that API usage is maximized</li>
						<li><em>Observation</em> for managing program impact and evolution</li>
						<li><em>Providing an API Platform</em> for providers and consumers to build on</li>
					</ul>
				</ul>
			</slide>
